{"tid":488313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[DQ之都] Daniel Abt香港Formula E 突被取消冠軍","createTime":"2017-12-03T14:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T23:24:11.000Z","uid":160094,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"10d8ef1e38a83e441a790132e60058ab71d229e9","tid":488313,"uid":160094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"2017/18 Formula E錦標賽香港站今天剛結束，第二回合由25歲今天生日的德國車手Daniel Abt勝出，唯FIA在晚上突然裁決，Daniel Abt的冠軍資格被取消。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/daniel-abt-hk-eprix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fdaniel-abt-hk-eprix.jpg&h=4affb20a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據稱他們在逆變器發現FIA安全貼紙，而引擎亦與原本所匯報的不一樣。有網民笑言：<span style=\"color: red;\">「Guys, welcome to Hong Kong. We always DQ the winner. 」</span>，歡迎來到香港，我們經常取消勝出者資格。Daniel Abt官方則表示，他們一定會上訴。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2017/12/daniel-abt-hk-eprix-disqualified/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2017%2F12%2Fdaniel-abt-hk-eprix-disqualified%2F&d=0uLJV8DI8brq%2BKz3LwaJap4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=09fb67ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2017/12/daniel-abt-hk-eprix-disqualified/</a>"},{"pid":"4c4108c2ef657ae263352b0d209ef68a8cac7ba7","tid":488313,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"True"},{"pid":"5c6bed0cdc09fb1f5cbf97cb21383980eb708771","tid":488313,"uid":54728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:16:45.000Z","msg":"柒出國際"},{"pid":"7aaf83f85c6d69cf347dc086a00ee9f5f2218d84","tid":488313,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164dc42835f0a722cd6e7169c7906b3dee75e0c3","tid":488313,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"